Rolex White Gold Stainless Steel Thunderbird Bezel Watch, Mid 1960''s

About the Item

FACTORY / HOUSE: Rolex Watch Company STYLE / REFERENCE: Oyster Perpetual / Thunderbird Bezel / Reference 1625 METAL / MATERIAL: Stainless Steel / 14Kt. White Gold Bezel DIMENSIONS: Length 42mm X Diameter 34mm CIRCA: Mid 1960''s MOVEMENT / CALIBRE: Perpetual Winding / 26 Jewels / Calibre 1560 DIAL / HANDS: Silvered w/ Silver Batons / Baton Hands ATTACHMENT / LENGTH: Original Jubilee Bracelet 20mm / Full Length WARRANTY: 18 months on the movement. LIFETIME SERVICE COMMITMENT This is a rare model with a 14Kt. solid gold bezel. It is sometimes called a Turn-O-Graph or a Thunderbird Datejust. The watch is in excellent condition and still has a factory rating on it. It is a sports style watch, good to wear with a casual style.
